## Interaction Contract

- Panel headers expose `role="button"`, `tabindex="0"`, `aria-expanded`, and `aria-controls`.
- Click, Enter, and Space use the same toggle path.
- `disabled` panels expose `aria-disabled="true"` and ignore pointer and keyboard toggles.

